prerequirements:
  - C/C++/Fortran compiler
  - cmake+make
  - netlib.org blas+cblas library
  - python (for the generator scripts)

optional:
  - additional BLAS libraries (Goto2, ATLAS, MKL, ...)
  - hardware accelerated versions of BLAS (cuda, clearspeed, opencl, ...)

directory structure:
  benchmarks/
   - linpack benchmark in order to test the library
  common/
   - python helper scripts
   - cmake modules
   - xml files
  library/
   - liftracc source code
   - auto generation scripts
   - profiling scripts
   - documentation
  testapps/
   - some test applications

